// TEST: Stack Scalars (rejects)
// stack is an ARRAY combinator: it adds an axis over arrays. Building a rank-1
// array out of scalars is the array literal's job, and the BL4004 message says
// so rather than silently accepting a second spelling of `[x, y]`.
let x = 1.0
let y = 2.0
let s = stack(x, y)
